<p><strong><em>Terrifying Glare.</em></strong> The scarecrow targets one creature it can see within 30 feet of it. If the target can see the scarecrow, the target must succeed on a DC 11 Wisdom saving throw or be magically frightened until the end of the scarecrowâ€™s next turn. The frightened target is paralyzed.</p>

